<br>
But with hair, almost all pros use mainly brushes to get those amazing long and smooth lines you see in most books.<br>
<br>
If you thought quills were a pain, wait until you try a brush.<br>
<br>
But if you keep practicing, the results can be outstanding. <p>I know it's asking for a lot, but please try to think before posting.<br>
